        #sponsor.section3
            h2 Sponsorship & Advertising
            p
                | Join Us! As a Festival Sponsor, your company will gain visibility among over 50,000 visitors,
                | including many well-educated, young, metropolitans with broad international backgrounds. Click #[a(href='participate_17_1053197596.pdf') here] to view the 2016 sponsorship levels.
            p
                The 2016 Festival of Nations offers an unparalleled opportunity to deliver your message of valuing diversity along with other key messages. We can customize your package to increase your Return on Investment!
            ul
                li Promote your brand
                li Feature a product
                li Build your customer base
                li Meet community leaders
                li Become identified with this exciting multicultural event!
            p
                Interested instead in advertising in our Festival of Nations program? **2016 advertising opportunities and rates coming soon!**
            p
